WF-003 | Reject application (Submitted and Pending Approval) | actor: <role> | branch: entity_state == Submitted and Pending Approval | terminal: Reject | on_success: rejects the application
WF-004 | Withdraw application (Submitted and Pending Approval) | actor: <role> | branch: entity_state == Submitted and Pending Approval | terminal: Withdraw Application | on_success: withdraws the application
WF-005 | Activate approved account (Approved) | actor: <role> | branch: entity_state == Approved | terminal: Activate | on_success: changes status to Active
WF-006 | Undo approval (Approved) | actor: <role> | branch: entity_state == Approved | terminal: Undo Approval | on_success: reverts to Submitted and Pending Approval status
WF-007 | Deposit into active account (Active) | actor: <role> | branch: entity_state == Active | terminal: Deposit | on_success: credits the account
WF-008 | Withdraw from active account (Active) | actor: <role> | branch: entity_state == Active | terminal: Withdraw | on_success: debits the account
